 歸園田居其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%BD-b%C3%A1t-b%C3%AD-th%C6%B0-bi%E1%BB%87t-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-GjoOrN8-c_Bl_LZTuan6vw">Tặng Lý bát bí thư biệt tam thập vận - 贈李八祕書別三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%AB-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-xZ1BB9vkb6BZXgwohAcJ2A">Trừ thảo - 除草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%A3n-t%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-lang-ki%E1%BA%BFn-qu%C3%A1-b%E1%BA%AFc-x%C3%A1/poem-I8ybcFas8OlQRoKmXWIogA">Vãn tình Ngô lang kiến quá bắc xá - 晚晴吳郎見過北舍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
